1 title searches, State Historic Preservation Office reviews, and wetlands
2 delineation.
3 …
4 "SECTION 11.12.(g) Agreements Required. – Monies may be disbursed from the Fund
5 previously appropriated for the Selectsite Readiness Program shall be transferred in full to
6 EDPNC when this act becomes law. Funds subsequently appropriated for the Program shall be
7 transferred in full to EDPNC once such an act becomes law. EDPNC may use funds only in
8 accordance with agreements entered into between EDPNC and a local government or a
9 government partnership. The agreement must include all of the performance criteria, remedies,
10 and other safeguards required to secure the assistance provided to ready the selectsite for a major
11 employer and must require EDPNC to recapture a proportionate amount of assistance provided
12 under this section for failure by a local government or government partnership to meet and
13 maintain the selectsite for availability for the purposes for which the assistance was provided.
14 …."
15 SECTION 2. This act is effective when it becomes law.
